description: Bogomolny equations of the abelian Higgs model. See JHEP 0407:008 (http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/0404022) for details.
Compute the metric in the modui space of solutions of the Bogomolny equations of the abelian Higgs model. See JHEP 0701:054 (http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/0610294) for more details.
